@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dsgrmg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.99 + v1 + 0.92)) + 0.95)
    v1 = (wp.abs(v1) / wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.69)))
    tmp = ((v1 - tmp) + wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.10 - v0 + 0.29)) / wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.13)))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (0.21 + v0)
    tmp = 1.00
    data[tid] = v0
